ation|K\u00f6ppen]] ''Dwb''), with bitterly cold and very dry winters, very warm, somewhat humid summers, and strong winds, especially in spring. The monthly 24-hour average temperature ranges from {{convert|\u221218.7|\u00b0C|1}} in January to {{convert|20.2|\u00b0C|1}} in July, with the annual mean at {{convert|2.05|\u00b0C|1}}. The annual precipitation is {{convert|325|mm|in|abbr=on}}, with more than half of it falling in July and August alone. With monthly percent possible sunshine ranging from 57% in July to 72% in October and February, sunshine is abundant year-round, there are 2,882 hours of bright sunshine annually.\n\n{{Weather box\n|location = West Ujimqin Banner (1981\u22122010 normals)\n|metric first = Y\n|single line = Y\n|collapsed =\n|Jan high C = \u221212.7\n|Feb high C =  \u22127.8\n|Mar high C =   0.5\n|Apr high C =  11.8\n|May high C =  19.2\n|Jun high C =  24.2\n|Jul high C =  26.2\n|Aug high C =  25.1\n|Sep high C =  19.4\n|Oct high C =  10.5\n|Nov high C =  \u22121.3\n|Dec high C =  \u22129.9\n\n|Jan mean C = \u221218.7\n|Feb mean C = \u221214.9\n|Mar mean C =  \u22126.3\n|Apr mean C =   4.4\n|May mean C =  12.0\n|Jun mean C =  17.6\n|Jul mean C =  20.2\n|Aug mean C =  18.5\n|Sep mean C =  11.9\n|Oct mean C =   3.1\n|Nov mean C =  \u22127.7\n|Dec mean C = \u221215.5\n\n|Jan low C = \u221223.9\n|Feb low C = \u221220.9\n|Mar low C = \u221212.6\n|Apr low C =  \u22122.5\n|May low C =   4.3\n|Jun low C =  10.5\n|Jul low C =  14.3\n|Aug low C =  12.2\n|Sep low C =   5.1\n|Oct low C =  \u22123.1\n|Nov low C = -13.0\n|Dec low C = \u221220.5\n|precipitation colour = green\n|Jan precipitation mm =  2.6\n|Feb precipitation mm =  2.7\n|Mar precipitation mm =  6.5\n|Apr precipitation mm =  9.4\n|May precipitation mm = 30.4\n|Jun precipitation mm = 56.8\n|Jul precipitation mm = 93.6\n|Aug precipitation mm = 67.5\n|Sep precipitation mm = 31.9\n|Oct precipitation mm = 13.6\n|Nov precipitation mm =  6.4\n|Dec precipitation mm =  3.6\n|year precipitation mm=325.